{
  "stem": "719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A white band-- it would say [NON-ENGLISH] or something like that-- with a hat, like a sailor's hat, with the thing here, and it-- and the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were supposed to help a transport-- or barge into in the middle of night in a building and knock in the doors.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were shocked, because some of those boys joined to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they didn't think of them being collaborators or helping the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were thinking that is a way of surviving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is a way I'm gonna manage through the war if-- if-- if I do that, or if I-- I'm not doing it for the Nazi.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm doing it for the-- the Jewish committee.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Jewish committee had meetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were contact.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They lived like kings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had access to transport to go places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But one thing I remember about-- in the beginning of the war-- because they were always picking on male-- on-- on-- on men, on Jewish men like my father.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A beard, or glasses, or looking Jewish was too much for them, especially-- they did it for fun.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some of the soldiers, the German soldiers, they would make fun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They would pick or hurt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we had-- this, I remember as a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father had a close friend, a doctor, a Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was still allowed to practice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he made a certificate out that my father, health-wise, is not able to stand in the line for a ration, for a bread or potatoes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I would be able, because I-- I volunteered. | said to my father, they're gonna hit you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They gonna to break your glasses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father was wearing heavy glasses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have a picture here.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
